  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add sashimi-cut bacon and cook until crispy, about 4 minutes.",
    "Add sliced green chilies and cook for an additional 2 minutes.",
    "Add grated ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add baby bok choy and cook until wilted, about 3 minutes.",
    "Pour in hoisin sauce, coconut aminos, and fresh lime juice. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the sauce to a simmer and cook for 2 minutes, until thickened.",
    "Stir in sesame seeds and chopped cilantro.",
    "Season with water to achieve desired consistency.",
    "Serve immediately and garnish with additional cilantro if desired."
